===验明正身===
2011年，二戰時期曾擔任女工的[[娜歐蜜·帕克·弗雷利|娜歐蜜·帕克·弗雷利]]參與了在{{link-en|鉚釘女工/第二次世界大戰家庭前線國家歷史公園|Rosie the Riveter/World War II Home Front National Historical Park}}舉辦的一場重聚聯歡會，並在那時認出了自己1942年時的照片<ref name=TIME>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/5114251/rosie-the-riveter-real-identity/|title=Everyone Was Wrong About the Real 'Rosie the Riveter' for Decades. Here’s How the Mystery Was Solved|magazine=Time|accessdate=2018-01-23|date=2018-01-23|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919104142/https://time.com/5114251/rosie-the-riveter-real-identity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她驚訝地發現，照片上標示的人名不是自己，而是另一位女工傑拉爾丁·道爾<ref name="NPR2">{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2018/01/23/580076619/naomi-parker-fraley-from-rosie-the-riveter-poster-dies-at-96|title=Naomi Parker-Fraley, From Rosie The Riveter Poster, Dies At 96|publisher=NPR|accessdate=2018-01-23|date=2018-01-23|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101100101/https://www.npr.org/2018/01/23/580076619/naomi-parker-fraley-from-rosie-the-riveter-poster-dies-at-96|dead-url=no}}</ref>。經過相關人士的努力與查證，最終她被認定為真正的原型。

==影响==
进入21世纪后，这张图像已经广为人知，所表达的信息也远远超出了其在二战期间的狭小定义。它出现在T恤、纹身、咖啡杯和冰箱磁贴上，种类如此繁多，以至于《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》称其是[[哥伦比亚特区|哥伦比亚特区]]最过度曝光的纪念项目<ref name="MythMisconception2006" />。2008年，图像被用来为[[2008年美国总统选举|总统选举]]中的两位女性热门人物[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]和[[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]大作宣传<ref name="CushingDrescher2009" />。[[米歇尔·奥巴马|米歇尔·奥巴马]]也被合成到了图像中并“现身”2010年10月30日哥伦比亚特区[[国家广场|国家广场]]上举行的一场聚会<ref name="Secrets2011" />。这张图像还被用在{{lang|en|Clorox}}公司家用清洁剂产品的商业广告上，照片中的女性左手上还戴有一个闪亮的结婚戒指<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thesocietypages.org/socimages/2007/10/22/trivializing-womens-power/ |last=Wade |first=Lisa |title=Sociological Images: Trivializing Women's Power |date=2007-10-22 |work=The Society Page |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622142929/http://thesocietypages.org/socimages/2007/10/22/trivializing-womens-power/ |archivedate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。对这一图像的模仿应用不仅限于知名女性，还包括男性、动物和虚构人物，另外还有相关的摇头和动作玩偶面世<ref name="MythMisconception2006" />。[[印第安纳波利斯|印第安纳波利斯]]的儿童博物馆中展示了一个长1.5米，宽1.2米，由数千颗糖果组成的复制品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://indianapolis-indiana.funcityfinder.com/2011/04/12/masterpieces-of-jelly-bean-art-collection/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007143948/http://indianapolis-indiana.funcityfinder.com/2011/04/12/masterpieces-of-jelly-bean-art-collection/ |archivedate=2012-10-07 |date=2011-04-12 |title=Masterpieces of Jelly Bean Art Collection at the Children’s Museum |last=Paul |first=Cindy |location=Indianapolis, Illinois |publisher=Funcityfinder.com |accessdate=2013-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jellybelly.com/Art_Gallery/bean_art_gallery.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003024420/http://jellybelly.com/Art_Gallery/bean_art_gallery.aspx |archivedate=2012-10-03 |title=We Can Do It! |work=Jelly Belly Bean Art Collection |last=Cumings |first=Kristen |publisher=Jelly Belly |accessdate=2013-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2010年6月，[[茱莉娅·吉拉德|茱莉娅·吉拉德]]当选为历史上首位女性[[澳大利亚总理|澳大利亚总理]]。[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]的一位自称凤凰的街头艺术家将吉拉德的脸张贴到了一张新的黑白版“我们能做到！”海报上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/4748630334/ |date=2010-06-29 |title=We Can Do It! |author=Phoenix |publisher=[[Flickr|Flickr]] |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007144521/http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/4748630334/ |archivedate=2012-10-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一本名叫《另一个》的杂志也于2010年7月刊登了从墨尔本一条街道上拍下的这张海报照片，照片显示海报右下角原本的“战争生产内部协调委员会”字样被换成了这位街头艺术家的{{lang|en|[[Flickr|Flickr]]}}照片组[[统一资源定位符|网址]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.anothermag.com/current/view/348/Australian_President_Julia_Gillard |title=Australian President, Julia Gillard |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100731090622/http://www.anothermag.com/current/view/348/Australian_President_Julia_Gillard |archivedate=2010-07-31 |date=2010-07-27 |work=AnOther Magazine |first=David |last=Hellqvist |accessdate=2013-06-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://damadesign.tumblr.com/post/866607274/julia-gillard-former-president-of-australia-as |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007144758/http://damadesign.tumblr.com/post/866607274/julia-gillard-former-president-of-australia-as |archivedate=2012-10-07 |date=2010-07-08 |title=Julia Gillard |author=Dama Design |publisher=Tumblr |accessdate=2013-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/5523564006/ |date=2011-03-12 |title=We Can Do It! |author=Phoenix |publisher=Flickr |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2017-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415220044/https://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/5523564006 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年3月，凤凰又制作了一个彩色的版本，右下角换成“她做到了！”的字样<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/4759196620/in/photostream/ |date=2010-07-02 |title=We Can Do It! |author=Phoenix |publisher=Flickr |accessdate=2013-05-29 |archive-date=2013-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218135548/http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/4759196620/in/photostream/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年，他又在海报上加上了醒目的“太伤心了”字样，来表示自己对澳大利亚政局发展的失望<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/6808410971/ |date=2012-01-23 |title=She Did It! (TOO SAD) |author=Phoenix |publisher=Flickr |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2017-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415012420/https://www.flickr.com/photos/phoenixthestreetartist/6808410971 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年12月，因當時還被認為是海報原型人物的傑拉尔丁·道爾逝世，《乌托读者》杂志提前定下了2011年1至2月的杂志封面，封面是对“我们能做到！”的一次戏仿，画面上动画片《[[辛普森一家|辛普森一家]]》中的家庭主妇[[玛琦·辛普森|玛琦·辛普森]]举起右手并紧握成拳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.utne.com/table-of-contents-january-february-2011.aspx |title=Table of Contents |work=Utne Reader |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120831085555/http://www.utne.com/table-of-contents-january-february-2011.aspx |archivedate=2012-08-31 |date=January–February 2011 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。杂志的编辑对道爾的去世表示遗憾，并认为她有可能是罗西这个角色的灵感来源<ref>{{cite web|url=http://utnereader.tumblr.com/post/2585298665 |title=untitled |work=Utne Reader editorial blog |date=2011-01-03 |publisher=Utne Reader |accessdate=2013-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130623045811/http://utnereader.tumblr.com/post/2585298665 |archivedate=2013-06-23 }}</ref>。

2011年上映的[[超级英雄|超级英雄]]电影《[[美国队长_(电影)|美国队长]]》片尾字幕时会出现“我们能做到！”的[[3D眼镜|立体图像]]，准确时间是英国女演员[[海莉·阿特维尔|海莉·阿特维尔]]的名字出现时<ref>{{cite web|title=Captain America: The First Avenger |url=http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/captain-america-the-first-avenger/ |work=Art of the Title |first=Lola |last=Landekic |date=2011-08-30 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130125184224/http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/captain-america-the-first-avenger/ |archivedate=2013-01-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

美国的一个名叫广告理事会的非盈利性组织声称，“我们能做到！”是由其前身战争广告委员会于1942年开发的，是“战时工作女性”宣传活动的一部分，让“超过200万女性”走进了军工厂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adcouncil.org/timeline.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070216085055/http://www.adcouncil.org/timeline.html |title=The Story of the Ad Council |publisher=Ad Council |archivedate=2007-02-16 |accessdate=2013-05-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adcouncil.org/About-Us/Frequently-Asked-Questions |title=Frequently Asked Questions |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130503040721/http://adcouncil.org/About-Us/Frequently-Asked-Questions |archivedate=2013-05-03 |publisher=Ad Council |accessdate=2013-06-23 |quote=Working in tandem with the Office of War Information, the Ad Council created campaigns such as Buy War Bonds, Plant Victory Gardens, 'Loose Lips Sink Ships,' and Rosie the Riveter's 'We Can Do it.' |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Conlon">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/peggy-conlon/happy-birthday-ad-council_b_1269338.html |last=Conlon |first=Peggy |title=Happy Birthday Ad Council! Celebrating 70 Years of Public Service Advertising |newspaper=Huffington Post |date=2012-02-13 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216044047/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/peggy-conlon/happy-birthday-ad-council_b_1269338.html |archivedate=2012-02-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2012年2月该理事会70周年庆时，一个由{{lang|en|[[Animax|Animax]]}}设计的交互式应用链接到了理事会的{{lang|en|[[Facebook|Facebook]]}}页面，这个应用允许用户将自己的头像张贴到“我们能做到！”中代替原本的头像，并且保存下来再进行发布分享<ref>{{cite web | url = http://pitchengine.com/helpsgood/helpsgood-develops-rosify-yourself-app-for-ad-councils-70th-birthday |title=HelpsGood Develops 'Rosify Yourself' App for Ad Council's 70th Birthday | publisher = HelpsGood | accessdate = 2013-06-23 | archivedate = 2013-06-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130623073219/http://pitchengine.com/helpsgood/helpsgood-develops-rosify-yourself-app-for-ad-councils-70th-birthday | deadurl = yes|date=2012年2月}}</ref>。理事会的首席执行官兼总裁佩姬·康伦也将自己的头像放在上面，之后与她所写的一篇有关理事会70年历史的文章一起发表在《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》上<ref name="Conlon" />。[[哥伦比亚广播公司|哥伦比亚广播公司]]《[[今天_(NBC)|今天]]》节目的两位职员也将电视台的两位新闻主播马特·劳尔和安·苏瑞的头像嵌入海报中发布在网站上<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.today.com/allday/plaza-sign-day-matt-rosie-riveter-1C9382427?franchiseSlug=alldaymain |title=Plaza sign of the day: Matt as Rosie the Riveter |last=Veres |first=Steve |date=2012-02-13 |work=Today |publisher=MSN Allday Today |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2019-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128020534/https://www.today.com/allday/plaza-sign-day-matt-rosie-riveter-1C9382427?franchiseSlug=alldaymain |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过，[[薛顿贺尔大学|薛顿贺尔大学]]教授詹姆斯·{{lang|en|J}}·金伯尔和[[匹兹堡大学|匹兹堡大学]]教授莱斯特·{{lang|en|C}}·奥尔森对海报的来源进行研究后认定，这张海报并非由战争广告委员会开发，也不是为了招聘女性员工<ref name="MythMisconception2006" />。

